# UI smoke run artifact (regenerated each run by tools/smoke.js)
tools/smoke-report.md

# Visual-diff harness — baseline/ is committed, current/ + diff/ + report are ephemeral
tools/visual-current/
tools/visual-diff/
tools/visual-diff-report.md

# css-probe harness — baseline.json is committed (the proof artifact), report is ephemeral
tools/css-probe-report.md

# CSS unused-selector scan output — regenerated each run by tools/scan-unused-css.js
tools/unused-css-report.md

# Harness state directory (seeded-fixture backups for view 14b / 03b / …).
# Files only exist between seedFeedbackFixture and restoreFeedbackBoard,
# plus leftover backups from crashed runs (recovered on next clean run).
tools/.harness-state/

# view-cascade-probe (Phase 3.6 !important-strip arbiter): the scripts are
# committed, but the baseline (~30MB), per-run keep-set, extracted candidate
# list, and flip reports are all regenerated each run.
tools/_view-cascade-baseline.json
tools/_view-cascade-report.md
tools/_view-important.json
tools/_keep-important.json
tools/_allstrip-flips.md
tools/_refine1-flips.md
